
This distribution includes two plugins: Kwiki::Purple and 
Kwiki::Purple::Sequence. The first requires the second.

If you have already installed the modules from CPAN or have
them in your SVN repository do this:

  $ cd /path/to/kwiki
  $ kwiki -add Kwiki::Purple::Sequence
  $ kwiki -add Kwiki::Purple

Otherwise you ca do this:

  $ cd /path/to/kwiki
  $ kwiki -install Kwiki::Purple::Sequence
  $ kwiki -install Kwiki::Purple

Keep in mind the Kwiki::Purple will alter the content of your
wiki pages in a way that will take some effort to revert. If
you are interested in experimenting with Kwiki::Purple, either
do so on an experimental wiki, or one where you won't mind
lots of purple nids in your pages.

